的措施，将香港的金融业发展至更高的台阶。 港股恒生指数午后跌幅扩大，一度跌至 2.8%，截至发稿，恒生指数报 29814.131，下跌 818.510，跌幅为 -2.67%。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picb.zhimg.com/50/v2-bb4c22ed9f878318ace53ab46abdde09_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "385 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/446103529"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8InKDVyLuxxp45EAMaCDYxNDEyNzczIKvM14EGMAc4gwdACHIJNDQ2MTAzNTI5eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "9_1614193419.9712505", "card_id": "Q_428842571", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 1972}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "我女朋友 27 了现在工作一月 5000 多，花钱没有概念，月月光甚至透支，该怎么劝她存钱？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "我每次劝她该存点钱了，她就说我花自己的钱有错吗，我买自己需要的东西有错吗，我都无言以对"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-5248340469f8617557310c5cdf2df3da_720w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "339 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/428842571"}}, "attached_info": "CkAInKDVyLuxxp45EAMaCDU3NTc3NzA1IJWki/0FMNwBOO4pQAlyCTQyODg0MjU3MXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "10_1614193419.9716341", "card_id": "Q_446108931", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 68}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何看待 2021 年 2 月 24 号 A 股大跌？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-2cf38de40b34a3ea9e408d4fbda66856_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "332 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/446108931"}}, "attached_info": "ClUInKDVyLuxxp45EAMaCDYxNDEzOTgwIOvb14EGMAM4jQJACnIJNDQ2MTA4OTMxeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQDyARMIARIPZG9tYWluX29wZXJhdG9y"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "11_1614193419.9719977", "card_id": "Q_445746439", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 60